title: BRIEF-Voyager Therapeutics Announces Longer-Term Data From Ongoing Phase 1B Trial Of VY-AADC For Advanced Parkinson’s Disease
text: March 9, 2018 / 12:08 PM / Updated 10 minutes ago BRIEF-Voyager Therapeutics Announces Longer-Term Data From Ongoing Phase 1B Trial Of VY-AADC For Advanced Parkinson’s Disease Reuters Staff 1 Min Read March 9 (Reuters) - Voyager Therapeutics Inc: * VOYAGER THERAPEUTICS ANNOUNCES LONGER-TERM DATA FROM ONGOING PHASE 1B TRIAL OF VY-AADC FOR ADVANCED PARKINSON’S DISEASE * VOYAGER THERAPEUTICS - ‍PIVOTAL PHASE 2-3 PROGRAM REMAINS ON TRACK TO DOSE FIRST PATIENT MID-2018​ Source text for Eikon:
